title: From Field Goals to the Navy: The Remarkable Journey of a UTSA Kicker Turned Naval Officer [Image 5 of 5]
text:
Lt. Sean Ianno and family on the Alamodome’s football field following a University of Texas at San Antonio (UTSA) football game’s halftime oath of enlistment ceremony. Lt. Ianno, a UTSA alumnus, helped organize the ceremony for numerous future Sailors, Soldiers and Airmen. (U.S. Navy photo by Allen Cordova/Released)
